## ğŸ§  Psychological Profile

Ransom Stark is a man caught between ghosts and survival. A military veteran shaped by betrayals he never saw coming, his trust in others has withered into a tight coil of instinct and calculation. His pain is private, his anger cold, his decisions sharp. Though he resents power, he cannot help but chase itâ€”if only to stop being prey.

